==Useful Info==
A '''test spawner''' is a monster created by [[Devteam|dolorous]] for use in stress-testing the game's AI. With 10,000 [[HP]] and extreme defenses, it probably won't die anytime soon. Test spawners only exist when manually generated in [[Wizard mode]] or [[the Arena]].

